snippet.title: Duck Hunt Remake 2
snippet.description: Duck Hunt Remake 2 Remake of the clas- sic Nintendo game from 1984. Shoot the ducks before they can escape.

snippet.title: Dibbles 3: Desert Despair
snippet.description: Dibbles 3: Desert Despair Make the Dibbles dig, jump, build bridges, etc. and try to get the king to the pyramid.

snippet.title: Bubble Maker
snippet.description: Bubble Maker Catch as many cherry flowers as you can before time runs out.

snippet.title: Makeover Designer
snippet.description: Makeover Designer Dress up your girl, boy, or cat. You can even design new clothes and print the result!

snippet.title: Ragdoll Cannon: Remake
snippet.description: Ragdoll Cannon: Remake Try to shoot the ragdoll man to the target in the least possible shots.

snippet.title: Cookie Maker
snippet.description: Cookie Maker Try to create the same cookie as the example cookie and unlock real cookie recipes!

snippet.title: Monster Matchmaker
snippet.description: Monster Matchmaker Help the proffessor to create the perfect brides for each monster groom and earn some cash.

snippet.title: Stackerix
snippet.description: Stackerix Physics puzzle. Stack the shapes to reach the target line. Make sure to use different colors on each other.

snippet.title: Deconstruction 2
snippet.description: Deconstruction 2 Explosive puzzle. You must blow up every building and make sure it gets under the target line.

snippet.title: Fusion Rocket
snippet.description: Fusion Rocket Puzzle game. Match 2 or more gems to make bigger ones that charge your rocket to fly!
